Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我村這四百餘年以來一直與世隔絕 自給自足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至節則是一個在夏至迎回祖先靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並祈求豐收的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日天亮就開始舉辦 一直會持續到後天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望諸位能夠過完這個節日再走不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看那邊的塔樓和窗戶的建築風格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是油畫裡的中世紀教堂一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 你看看這板壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還有口古井呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹啥打槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的山裡有野狼出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個村子裡的人不是狼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼話 我們可是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與山外之人確實不同種族…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼和考迪利亞長得一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然當時我還只是個孩子 但是我卻記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何曼尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人考迪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對老爺而言 對村子而言 都是個無法磨滅的災星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何曼尼婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.63,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,545)}夏至節神明降旨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案子是發生在特奧多爾老爺的書房裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚12點正 女僕會去書房伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候考迪利亞還只有15歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時讓她去把水壺裡的水換了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也正好是在午夜十二點去辦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道是十二點「正」？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時有其他人在場 我們目擊了她用鑰匙開門進房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我用懷錶看過時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知為何 其他人的證言裡時間都不統一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考迪利亞進了書房沒一會兒就尖叫著跑了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跑去一看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才發現特奧多爾老爺已經被人用短刀刺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知為何 地上卻散了一地的金幣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金幣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 村裡平常不用金幣來買賣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以平常都是由特奧多爾老爺來保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那晚開始 考迪利亞就高燒臥床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她退燒之後 繼任村長的我就把她逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐出村子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時她隨身的東西 僅剩下一個金幣和一個行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她一離開大門 我們馬上收起了吊橋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個黃花大閨女 沒有離開過村子一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們是有些擔心她能不能自己過活…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人不能留在村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會為村裡招災的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現如今考迪利亞的女兒卻回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 妳等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛到不久妳就說要去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去散步嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是村長謝吉吾思的助手 叫做安布羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只是想搞清楚 你皮膚和眼睛的顏色為何與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也清楚外面的人不都是金髮碧眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能帶我去一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 我希望能多摸摸這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您 那麼您希望去哪裡看看呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是考迪利亞從前的住處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是怕被人知道帶外人來這裡 會惹禍上身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也沒寫字啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是考迪利亞小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孩提時代的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 考迪利亞小姐不是15歲才被趕出村子的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明曾有人來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人帶走了之前存放在這裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且用這張成人後的考迪利亞的照片來替換了這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片混沌有指向性嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特奧多爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是前任村長的墳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以對墳墓做出這樣不敬的舉動…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我並非罪人 C」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是考迪利亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定是考迪利亞寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親果然是遭人冤枉而被趕出村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 誰才是罪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是和維多利嘉的眼睛一樣的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我放水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再玩一盤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給錢我可以考慮放水喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 電話怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們兩個小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…米爾德瑞德小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這裡有電話 就說明其實這裡通了電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 村長明明說這裡自給自足…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得奇怪 就問了那個有點神經兮兮的女僕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像有個贊助者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊助者？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫啥名來著的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫啥布萊恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 是個叫布萊恩·羅斯科的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩·羅斯科…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人似乎是離開村子的人的後代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說10年前他就出過資了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 打牌也打膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去教堂看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才外面有狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼來了那個討厭的老村長會幫我們趕走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 我們去玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 衣服又皺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這身打扮蕾絲花邊實在太多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前布萊恩·羅斯科來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟有何目的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該是來村裡架設電線的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前那可是世界大戰剛剛打響的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種年代裡 為何還要不慌不忙地到小山村裡通電線呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前的話 那張照片的拍攝年代就說得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是洗澡水 請摻冷水慢慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 有事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我人就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛洗澡皮膚好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原來是在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎維多利嘉也恢復常態了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 裡面沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 久城 你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 妳沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有人想要恐嚇我 來把我趕出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧 這村裡一股陰森的氣氛 讓人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會保護我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了 這是紅蕪菁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車子是冬軍的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上的男人們會扮演冬夏兩軍來模擬打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏軍會把冬軍的頭領冬之男打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把大車點火燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想侮辱本村的話就請離開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊啊 都這個時代了還講迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子也太那啥了 你說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 要是現在被趕出村子的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那個…這傢伙就是嘴上沒口德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回房去吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人昨晚就在教堂裡胡鬧來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當著村裡人的面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裝飾在牆上的酒壺扔進了聖水盆裡 好大的動靜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉鬼哪裡還會講道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在那裡嗤笑說為啥要看重這種破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己才是最看重古董的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 給妳拿了些節日點心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是亞蘭先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嘴上那樣說 他也是喜歡熱鬧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這個是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是安布羅斯先生嗎？挺帥氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之男 化為灰燼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙人怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿水來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞蘭先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他想要妨礙節日 所以自己和紙人調換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這客人真是傻得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝吉吾思村長 這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當姑娘們扔榛子的時候 這個人正經過廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時廣場上人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為他不可能和紙人調換過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過猶不及 多言傷身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至節不能因此中止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來要去教堂主持儀式 就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有人死了 但是慶祝卻不停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子果然很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是嗎 維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 維多利嘉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會保護我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌先生 你也來這裡諮詢未來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當夏軍勝利 豐收有了保障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂就會一直空到傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為教堂是連著那個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來觀戰的祖先的靈魂也會經過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他們走之前 祖先的靈魂會借村長之口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來回答孩子們的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌先生 難得來一次 來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我還要找維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 安布羅斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 我在找維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是找她 那大可不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那女孩與你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想問些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 我就只有她一個朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我能和維多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不會死在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是數年之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會掀起一股席捲世界的潮流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個根基未穩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕會因為那陣潮流而各奔東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的心會一直連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也來這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳問了啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問了我會不會再長個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這都問的啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被說了好大一通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生啥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是 不說一聲就不知跑到哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛才去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去書房了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人考迪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這樣從背後刺了老爺一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到短刀的刀柄沒入…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「可老爺是個成年人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「考迪利亞才15歲 身高差得太多了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將短刀完全插入成年人的背部 小孩子是無法夠到也無法做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是她就成了罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂被打上了骯髒的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人另有其人的話…妳是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧之泉已經傾訴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片完全重構之時來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說被完全重構了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳已經知道誰是犯人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使知道犯人 我也沒有證據…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使出了人命 即使狼也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至節也絕不能中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經聽不見狼的聲音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了 安布羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現世的罪煌煌泛光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的罪被其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼我有種很不好的預感…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.97,0:24:29.98,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}故國中吠聲響徹
